Directory structure
===================
   test_2d_gc_polar_one_mu         -- executable
   gcsim2d_polar_one_mu_input.nml  -- input file
   README                   -- info (this file)
   run/                     -- output directory

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, and move into it
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run

1. Run simulation within directory
     $ ../test_2d_gc_polar_one_mu ../gcsim2d_polar_one_mu_input


